GVizRhizosphere
public static class GVizRhizosphere.Options
extends com.google.gwt.visualization.client.AbstractDrawOptions

Configuration options for the visualization.

Use RhizosphereOptions to define configuration options and then invoke the wrap(RhizosphereOptions) method to convert them to the proper type required by the Google Visualization APIs.
